# List of State Register of Heritage Places in the Shire of Donnybrook-Balingup

The State Register of Heritage Places is maintained by the Heritage Council of Western Australia. , 113 places are heritage-listed in the Shire of Donnybrook-Balingup, of which twelve are on the State Register of Heritage Places.
List
The Western Australian State Register of Heritage Places, , lists the following twelve state registered places within the Shire of Donnybrook-Balingup:
